node.title: Body found in search for missing kayaker
node.description: Police have located a body in Wellington Harbour this evening believed to be that of missing kayaker Jack Skellett.
node.content:
["Police have located a body in Wellington Harbour this evening believed to be that of missing kayaker Jack Skellett.", "", "
\nPhoto: Supplied / NZ Police\n
", "Search teams today had been searching for the missing 23-year-old after he failed to return to shore.", "He was reported overdue around 10pm on Monday.", "In a statement this evening police extended sympathy to the man's family, who they said had requested privacy.", "The matter will be referred to the Coroner."]
